    • Method Detail

      • finalizeSetup

        void finalizeSetup()
        Called by GlobalSetup on components once all components have been registered. Don't call it yourself, just implement it to do stuff that can only be done once all components are registered, or leave it empty if your component has nothing to do at that time.
